What this does:
When you use UITableViews and you click a cell: 
  - show an indicator in the accessoryType
  - show the NetworkActivityIndicator
  - Disable clicking of the button
  - Call didSelectRowAtIndexPath:(NSIndexPath *)indexPath inBackground:(Boolean)background;
  - Reset everything

CREATING a static libray on the iPhone using another Xcode project:
  - http://www.amateurinmotion.com/articles/2009/02/08/creating-a-static-library-for-iphone.html

Using categories from a library with iPhone: 
  - http://developer.apple.com/library/mac/#qa/qa2006/qa1490.html
Use the "Other linker flags" option: -all_load